title: SSEN Transmission TEC – Transmission Entry Capacity Register
description:
A list of SSEN Transmission projects that hold contracts for Transmission Entry Capacity (TEC) with NESO.


These include existing and future connection projects and projects that can be directly connected to the National Electricity Transmission System (NETS), or make use of it.


To view or download this data, please register or login.


For the full UK TEC Register, please see the bi-weekly publication from NESO here.
tags: TEC, Generation, Contracted, Connect, Date, Capacity, Developer, Location

title: NESO Condition C17 Statement Consultation Report to Authority 2024-2025
description:
This dataset contains data that details the network performance of SSEN Transmission including availability, faults and reliability for 2024-2025.


To download the NESO report and SSEN Transmission's raw data worksheet feeding the report, please go to the 'export' tab > 'alternative exports'.
tags: Availability, Faults, Energy Not Supplied, Reliability, System Performance, Performance, C17

For the full UK Interconnector Register, please see the bi-weekly publication from NESO here.
